Type: Package
Package: varr
Title: Utility Functions for VAR Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Semião", , "ricardo.semiao@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ricardo Semião e Castro <ricardo.semiao@outlook.com>
Description: Utility functions for VAR models. Currently, ggplots for 
    objects like like IRF's, FEVD's, predict graphs, and residual 
    analysis. Soon to contain functions for common tests and statistics,
    support for other VAR-like objects, and unified builders for vector
    regression models.
